title: Jessica Simpson Can’t Really Pull It Off [Jessica Simpson]
author: Christy Frink
contentEncoded:
With her brand spankin’ new country album hitting the shelves yesterday, not-so-Nashvillian Jessica Simpson was making the morning show rounds performing hit single “Come On Over.” In this clip from Tuesday morning’s Good Morning America, we see Jessica doing her best country impression, and while we’re happy to see that she’s ditched the cowboy getup she was seen sporting at LAX this summer, but we’re not convinced that she’ll ever be able to pass herself off as “a country girl at heart.”
